race.description: The Lids Fly On Ladbrokes Live Channels
race.comment: LIGNITE COAL (4) produced a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 300m behind Shipley's Girl (18.21) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. TANGLES TIPPETT (2) resumed in a Grade 5 at this track and finished seventh over 300m (18.43). Sure to be fitter. Form from his last run is proving strong. Has ability and is one of the better chances. WITCH ROLEX (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (32.16) in a Mix at this track. Shapes as one to consider. HIDDEN SECRET (3) can sneak into the finish.
